{"pin":"ABU0826","subcodes":[{"code":"ABU0826","anchor":"","title":"Words to the Baha'is, spoken on 1912-12-03","first_line":"Praise be to God that Mrs Krug has been the cause of your gathering in this meeting where you are engaged in mentioning God and in adducing proofs…. O Lord! We are weak; strengthen us","first_line_orig":"حمد خدا را که مسس کروگ سبب اجتماع شما و انعقاد چنین محفلی گردیده که به ذکر الهی... خدایا ما ضعیفیم تو قوی کن ما نادانیم تو دانا فرما خدایا فقیریم  ","language":"3","word_count":"360","subjects":"@prayer for spiritual recognition, @spiritual transformation, @teaching the Cause; call to teach, @divine grace, bounty, confirmations; spiritual capacity","translations":[{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"hi","lang_name":"Hindi"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"te","lang_name":"Telugu"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"vi","lang_name":"Vietnamese"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"ms","lang_name":"Malay"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"diu","lang_name":"Rugciriku"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"hr","lang_name":"Croatian"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"}]},{"code":"ABU0826GOD","anchor":"god","translations":[{"language":"ms","lang_name":"Malay"}]},{"code":"ABU0826LOR","anchor":"lor","translations":[{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"lo","lang_name":"Lao"},{"language":"gu","lang_name":"Gujarati"},{"language":"mr","lang_name":"Mara